<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Schedule Cancelled Notification</title>
</head>
<body>
  <p>Dear <%= @client.name %>,</p>
  <p>We regret to inform you that your schedule for the 
    <ul>
      <% @schedule.treatments.each do |treatment| %>
        <li><%= treatment.name %></li>
      <% end %>
    </ul> on <%= @schedule.date.strftime('%d-%m-%Y') %> has been cancelled.
  </p>
  <p>If you have any questions or would like to reschedule, please contact us.</p>
  <p>Thank you for your understanding.</p>
</body>
</html>